A function that returns a
[`dose()`](https://openpharma.github.io/crmPack/reference/dose.md)
method that computes the dose reaching a specific target value of a
given independent variable, based on the model specific parameters.

## Arguments

- model:

  (`GeneralModel` or `ModelPseudo`)

  (`integer`)  
  the toxicity grade for which the dose function is required
